# Aquarius One Supercomputer ☢️

## The New Clear Revolution: 2 Particles, 1 String

**Spherical Immersion-Cooled Supercomputer with Dual-Axis Positioning and Free-Space Optical Networking**

### Mission

Ocean restoration powered by breakthrough fusion technology. Clean the oceans, heal the planet, spread life across the galaxy.

### Performance

- **16.4 exaFLOPS** peak performance (GPU configuration)
- **4,096 compute nodes** in 10-meter sphere
- **40-50 MW** power consumption
- **PUE 1.05-1.20** (most efficient datacenter design ever)
- **5-minute hot-swap** panel maintenance without shutdown

### Innovation

- **Water immersion cooling** eliminates traditional cooling infrastructure
- **Dual-axis positioning** enables access to any panel without draining
- **Free-space optical networking** through water medium (1+ petabit/sec)
- **Integration with CSG fusion reactors** for closed-loop energy systems
- **Icosahedral geometry** inspired by viral capsid structures

### Applications

- Ocean plastic cleanup optimization
- Climate modeling and restoration planning
- Desert reforestation coordination
- Marine ecosystem restoration
- Scientific simulation and AI training

### Technical Documentation

Complete patent-quality specifications available in 5 parts:

- **Part 1**: Core system description
